e="preserve">Yulia Vitalievna Rudenko (born Yulia Guzeva on 26 May 1990 in Krasnodar) is a Russian rugby union player, and 2014 rugby sevens champion. She participated at the 2014 Rugby Europe Women's Sevens Grand Prix Series, and 2016 Rugby Europe Women's Sevens Grand Prix Series, and 2016 European Rugby Championship, and 2019–20 Rugby Europe Championships.
She plays for Krasny Yar.
